{"tid":1422044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做乜無啦啦打9人！ 真係唔好因一時衝動毀左個運動！","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:43:43.000Z","uid":59454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39a95cd4345cea31b566702c7835d83f88361176","tid":1422044,"uid":59454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:38:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/156468627834558/posts/1435489773265764?s=100001561851853&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F156468627834558%2Fposts%2F1435489773265764%3Fs%3D100001561851853%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Lhg6HStjEOrAYLon%2F%2F44JwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=5ce53226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/156468627834558/posts/1435489773265764?s=100001561851853&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n利申翻一直有發夢出去 睇開立場 蘋果 但同時亦有follow講人講地 HKG報呢啲藍絲新聞去接收多啲方面既資訊 睇下反對者有咩意見 了解下佢地諗法<br />\n<br />\n話說平時見到佢地既post一直都係得啖笑 採取冷處理既辦法 但今日見到呢段片個靚仔走去一拳打落個阿伯到 我覺得係有需要去講一講！<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住 你地所有既行動代表既唔係你地自己 係代表緊我地所有人 我明白有時係會好嬲 尋日港鐵不合作我都比人屌足全日 但要記住面對住呢啲人打佢地係唔會令佢地醒 只會為我地增加不必要既輿論壓力 要分清楚乜時候應該郁手 乜時候係應該冷靜 唔好比噴怒沖昏頭腦 <br />\n<br />\n請記住我地最初出黎既目的 同時唔好成為我地最討厭既人！ 打人個靚仔如果睇到希望你認真諗下 唔係想批評你 只係想提醒你 同時提醒大家！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割席 <br />\n不篤灰 <br />\n大陸dum原子筆落黎都唔割<br />\n</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後辛苦大家 我地一齊撐落去！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d460e19c643e8857b8a0e6d3f580288aea1afe09","tid":1422044,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"[懶人包]黑警記者會重點及拆招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65c3df8a2d9034a60a0f44a630158a09df5b9e4c","tid":1422044,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"原子筆我唔驚喎"},{"pid":"228eeb05729df744f1538cccd4e7b3135fb0b591","tid":1422044,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"陳伯單野點計"},{"pid":"4089f154c0f8e5aef460bad6410228e247f1eb4e","tid":1422044,"uid":59454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c3df8a2d9034a60a0f44a630158a09df5b9e4c","tid":1422044,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"原子筆我唔驚喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"大陸原子筆勁過原子彈你唔係依家先知下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee1dc6587030b93b479e04363d390446684e0dc","tid":1422044,"uid":59454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"228eeb05729df744f1538cccd4e7b3135fb0b591","tid":1422044,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"陳伯單野點計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"我地屌9警察打陳伯 所以我地更加唔好做同佢地一樣既野"}]}